{"tid":1753853,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"前兩日整咗個黃店hashtag 之後比IG ban咗","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T04:50:25.000Z","uid":221748,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"84ba80b53c00950c586ee10e1734346d0924c21e","tid":1753853,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"話說我前幾日整咗個黃店hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁方便大家搵野食<br />\n之後仲放咗係Bio 等大家都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypVW5AB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypVW5AB.png&h=78a620a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後過二日發現比IG ban 咗，全部post 既hashtag 都失效晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後更誇張係連tag location 都唔會顯示出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比圖大家睇下 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtgfBJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtgfBJO.png&h=e56b14aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5jpu3P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5jpu3P.png&h=28d7b1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連本身自己個Tag都冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網話係因為比人report ,宜家過咗四五日都仲係咁<br />\n求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人ban完 個reach都大跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?igshid=1kebf69mk029t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffoodkiller_dk%3Figshid%3D1kebf69mk029t&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM295Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=c1581631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?igshid=1kebf69mk029t</a>"},{"pid":"5c819ad1f9b5ebc5d120284560395d7036a0c600","tid":1753853